{"tid":863764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風鋸樹都比人屌。","createTime":"2018-10-16T00:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T00:55:30.000Z","uid":11779,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d193213e5149552c79a796333a91df839f228004","tid":863764,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOURXtH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOURXtH.jpg&h=a1907785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山竹黎到時連健康嘅樹都吹跌，更何況呢棵樹啲根已經嚴重腐爛。隔離就係宿舍， 咁大棵樹如果壓親人點算？係咪佢負責？<br />\n<br />\n香港攝影師9成垃圾黎，自己影相搞到烏煙瘴氣 為左幅相係深夜用光射雀射螢光蟲就就合理，人地係打風前鋸樹就天理不容，定係呢啲人覺得以後冇影呢棵樹就好似殺佢父母咁？<br />\n<br />\n係呢班人眼中影相原來重要過其他人條命。"},{"pid":"90a4876038b4fffee59769e6156adc96d18bd216","tid":863764,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:30:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52160e4d87d83397038b7f203cfd8850792b41f2","tid":863764,"uid":11779,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:31:50.000Z","msg":"鋸又屌 唔鋸壓親人又上街。"},{"pid":"3efae17d42f03bd18a423e973119eb01c149c1f1","tid":863764,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90a4876038b4fffee59769e6156adc96d18bd216","tid":863764,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:30:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"膠少陣"},{"pid":"03252c7154cf503a7f50474fc58d1e7b43233290","tid":863764,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"做乜無啦啦post舊相<br />\n<br />\n有冇野證明啲根嚴重腐爛？"},{"pid":"101d2fa7dbfd8131bd790ca1c2d50722b79a4031","tid":863764,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03252c7154cf503a7f50474fc58d1e7b43233290","tid":863764,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"做乜無啦啦post舊相<br />\n<br />\n有冇野證明啲根嚴重腐爛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:35